FRED NYSTROM

Fred joined the Klahanie staff in May, 2018 following five years as the Executive Director for a local nonprofit helping people with developmental disabilities. He has raised his family in Issaquah for the past 35 years. Fred continues to be active in Rotary and other civic organization.
